OL,6,FA man who had been told not to drive
OL,7,Fdue to his epilepsy has been jailed
OL,8,Fafter causing a fatal crash following
OL,9,Fa seizure at the wheel.
OL,11,FA judge said Peter Gibson, 63,
OL,12,F"gambled with the lives of others"
OL,13,Fwhen he made the decision to drive his
OL,14,Fwife's car despite his medical
OL,15,Fcondition.
