OL,3,CDriver caused fatal crash after
OL,4,Cignoring epilepsy warnings
OL,6,FGibson, of Armstrong Place West,
OL,7,FGrimsby, had his wife in the Nissan
OL,8,FDuke when he collided with a Jaguar
OL,9,Fcar carrying 25-year-old Cosmin Rostas
OL,10,Fon Freeman Street in Grimsby 20
OL,11,FDecember 2022.
OL,13,FMr Rostas died in hospital.
OL,15,FGibson admitted causig death by
OL,16,Fdangerous driving and was jailed for
OL,17,Ffour years.
OL,19,FJudge John Thackray KC told him: "You
OL,20,Fliterally gambled with the lives of
OL,21,Fothers."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/9
