OL,6,FJeremy Evans, prosecuting, told Hull
OL,7,FCrown Court Gibson had been advised
OL,8,Fnot to drive but "ignored this and
OL,9,Fmade no disclosure to the DVLA," about
OL,10,Fhis epilepsy. He also failed to tell
OL,11,Fthe couple's insurers.
OL,13,F"This wasn't the first time that he
OL,14,Fhad taken to driving a vehicle
OL,15,Fillegally," Mr Evans said.
