OL,6,FAfter suffering the seizure, Gibson
OL,7,Fcaused the car to accelerate sharply.
OL,8,FIt went through red traffic lights and
OL,9,Fcollided with the Jaguar, despite
OL,10,Fattempts by Gibson's wife to steer it
OL,11,Fout of the way.
OL,13,FMr Rostas asked if he was going to die
OL,14,Fas he was cut from the wreckage and
OL,15,Fwas taken to the Diana, Princess of
OL,16,FWales Hospital in Grimsby but died a
OL,17,Fshort time later.
OL,19,FGibson's wife suffered injuries to her
OL,20,Fpelvis and a fracture to her lower
OL,21,Fback.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/9
