OL,3,CDriver caused fatal crash after
OL,4,Cignoring epilepsy warnings
OL,6,FGibson told police at the scene: "It
OL,7,Fwas down to me having a fit, mate."
OL,9,FHe later said that he had suffered
OL,10,Ffrom epilepsy for 30 years.
OL,12,F"It's clearly not the first time that
OL,13,Fhe has driven with this known medical
OL,14,Fcondition," Mr Evans said.
OL,16,FMr Rostas, who was from Romania, had a
OL,17,Fson and two daughters, including one
OL,18,Fwho was not born at the time of the
OL,19,Fcrash.
