OL,6,FThe family had suffered "major
OL,7,Ffinancial difficulties" because of his
OL,8,Fdeath, the court heard.
OL,10,FStephen Robinson, mitigating for
OL,11,FGibson, said: "He knows he should not
OL,12,Fhave been driving and he bitterly
OL,13,Fregrets that decision. He knows that,
OL,14,Fif he had not driven, a young man
OL,15,Fwould still be alive with his family."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G6/9
