OL,6,FJudge Thackray told Gibson: "It was
OL,7,Fonly good fortune that there was only
OL,8,Fone fatality. There could so easily
OL,9,Fhave been many more, including your
OL,10,Fwife. This was quite simply an
OL,11,Faccident waiting to happen.
OL,13,F"You should not have been behind the
OL,14,Fwheel and you knew that. You ended a
OL,15,Flife and you have brought lifelong
OL,16,Fgrief and misery to his family. It's
OL,17,Fextremely sad."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G7/9
