OL,6,FHe added: "It was entirely predictable
OL,7,Fand an accident waiting to happen. You
OL,8,Fwere well aware that you should not
OL,9,Fhave been driving because of the risk
OL,10,Fof a seizure and it was a risk that
OL,11,Fyou took that day and on other
OL,12,Foccasions."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G8/9
