OL,6,FAfter the hearing, Sgt Rob Mazingham,
OL,7,Fof Humberside Police, said: "This case
OL,8,Fhighlights the necessity to declare
OL,9,Fmedical conditions and not to get
OL,10,Fbehind the wheel of a vehicle if you
OL,11,Fhave them. It highlights the
OL,12,Fconsequences of a decision not to
OL,13,Fdeclare them. It takes only a second
OL,14,Fand one bad decision to ruin so many
OL,15,Flives."
